Kiseki.Kiseki/Common/Keyword/Link_Desc:
For linked targets:
When one attacks, the other has a 50% chance to perform a follow-up attack with 45% Attack Power (follow-up attacks cannot trigger additional attacks);
When one takes damage, if the other has more than 50% health, there's a 50% chance to reduce that damage to 80% and share the damage.

